<h1>Appointment Confirmed!</h1>

<p>Hi {{customerName}},</p>

<p>
    Great news! Your appointment has been successfully booked. We're looking forward to meeting with you.
</p>

<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Appointment Details</h3>
    <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{formatDate startTime "long"}} at {{formatDate startTime "time"}}</p>
    <p><strong>Duration:</strong> {{duration}} minutes</p>
    <p><strong>Quote Number:</strong> {{quoteNumber}}</p>
    <p><strong>Appointment ID:</strong> {{appointmentId}}</p>
</div>

{{#if meetingLink}}
<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #dbeafe; border-left-color: #3b82f6;">
    <h3>Join Meeting</h3>
    <p>
        {{#if hasGoogleMeet}}
        Your appointment will take place via Google Meet. You can join the meeting using the link below:
        {{else}}
        Your appointment meeting link:
        {{/if}}
    </p>
    {{> button text="Join Meeting" url=meetingLink}}
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; margin-top: 16px;">
        <strong>Meeting Link:</strong><br>
        <a href="{{meetingLink}}" style="color: #3b82f6; word-break: break-all;">{{meetingLink}}</a>
    </p>
    {{#if hasGoogleMeet}}
    <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">
        A calendar invitation has been sent to your email with this meeting link.
    </p>
    {{/if}}
</div>
{{/if}}

<h2>What to Expect</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Before the meeting:</strong> Please review your quote details and prepare any questions</li>
    <li><strong>During the meeting:</strong> We'll discuss the project scope, timeline, and answer your questions</li>
    <li><strong>After the meeting:</strong> You'll receive an invoice and we'll schedule the work to begin</li>
</ul>

{{#if appointmentDescription}}
<div class="info-box">
    <h3>Appointment Notes</h3>
    <p>{{appointmentDescription}}</p>
</div>
{{/if}}

<div class="info-box" style="background-color: #fef3c7; border-left-color: #f59e0b;">
    <h3>Important Reminders</h3>
    <ul style="margin: 8px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
        <li>Please join the meeting 5 minutes early to test your connection</li>
        <li>Have your quote details handy for reference</li>
        <li>If you need to reschedule or cancel, please contact us at least 24 hours in advance</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<h2>Need to Make Changes?</h2>
<p>
    If you need to reschedule or cancel this appointment, please contact us as soon as possible:
    <br>
    Phone: <strong>{{organizationPhone}}</strong>
    <br>
    Email: <strong>{{organizationEmail}}</strong>
</p>

<p>
    We're excited to work with you!
</p>

<p>
    Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The {{organizationName}} Team</strong>
</p>